data.description: This home price just got better!  Looking for a personal residence or investment opportunity? This home offers versatile potential allowing to configure it as a 4 or 5 bedroom or opt for a 4 bedroom layout w/the flexibility of an office or game room. Kitchen is open to the family room (sink has reverse osmosis water system). Home has volume ceilings, open floor plan, and a large gorgeous lanai area. The backyard features a newer caged SALTWATER (heated) pool with sun deck (2021) and is truly exceptional! Discover the charm of a firepit located just off the caged pool area creating a cozy, inviting space for outdoor gatherings. Ample fenced-in backyard space provides privacy & versatility for various outdoor activities.Close to shopping and dining. Newer exterior paint, roof (Sept 2023), stainless appliances, and vinyl fencing.  Home has manual hurricane shutters. Owners state there was NO water intrusion from hurricane Ian.  Great location in Cape Country Club area. Sellers are in the process (Jan 22-27th) of having the interior professionally painted neutral colors. (Walls/ceilings/baseboards/kitchen cabinets). Seller are relocating due to job transfer and are motivated.
